NIXOS
Back up all your important config/files
make sure nothing is missing (this only changes configuration.nix

$git clone https://github.com/sekoloton/nix-hyprland 
$cd nix-hyprland
$sudo mv configuration.nix /etc/nixos/ #make sure configuration.nix has been backed up / deleted!!
$sudo nixos-rebuild switch
$reboot

and Hyprland is ready, for the appearance you can take it from github or make it yourself
